parameters: Whoa--!? What's with this octopus!? It's huge...!?

(What should I do...! I've never seen such a big octopus
before. If I took it to a zoo, it might sell for a lot)
Aaahh! Ouch! The tentacles are attacking me!?

Can't be helped. Looks like I have to defeat it! If it's
coming at me, I'll chop it up and turn it into vinegar
octopus!
--The ghost octopus and its tentacles are attacking!
This is the end for you! Take this!!

I did it! I chopped up the tentacles! The sword skills I
learned from my father aren't just for show!

Hey hey hey...! I heard a rumbling from the cave, so I came
to check it out...!?

What the heck!? Karin, what are you fighting? This huge
monster, could it be an octopus!?

Everyone, don't come any closer! This octopus can regenerate
its legs, we can't defeat it!

What did you say!? Even Karin-san can't defeat it? Then we
have no choice but to run! Hurry over here!

No! The tentacles are wrapping around my whole body...! I...
can't escape...!

Damn it! That octopus bastard is trying to dive underwater!
If this continues, Karin-san will be dragged into the sea!
~~~~~! (Such incredible strength...! I can't break free...!)

Joyous joyous... Karin. It seems your triumphant march ends
here, doesn't it?

Hmph... What are you laughing at...? You blame me for being
exiled, don't you? You must still hold a grudge against me
in your heart.

That's not it... When we first met again, that was certainly
the case. However... Living on that island and this escape
have made me feel a strange connection with you all. If I
had stayed with the cult, I would never have known such
things--

--! Stop showing off and run away already! While I'm acting
as a decoy, get on the ship and escape from this island!

Escaping would be easy but--... It wouldn't be a problem to
control this octopus, would it?

The promise I made with you was 'never to cast spells on
humans again'-- but an octopus is a mollusk! If it's not
human, there's no problem, right?
No good! The tentacles are reaching for Kokuyou Tengu-san--!
Run! You'll be taken away to the sea along with Karin-san!

You ghostly octopus-- take this, the culmination of the
techniques I've honed betting my life! Muuuuunnn!!

--Kokuyou Tengu has cast a hypnotic spell on the ghostly
octopus!
It suddenly became docile...? What's going on?

--Eh? The tentacles are caressing my body...! That place
is...!?

--Yaaah! Ahahaha! Don't tickle the soles of my feet! Eee!
It's ticklish! Eeeeek~~~!!

Nyohoho! This is payback for destroying my cult. Enjoy a
little tickle torture for a while

--! Seriously, that's amazing! Lord Kokuyou Tengu, you've
managed to control the ghostly octopus...! You really are no
ordinary being, huh?

That's great. Anyway, we're saved. It would have been a
shame to be eaten by an octopus after all the trouble of
escaping from the island.

Well, that's enough revenge on Karin for now. I went easy on
her. Now, what to do with this helpful octopus--

Can't it replace the broken ship? If it's this big, we can
ride on its back across the sea. It can also serve as
emergency food.

Hmm. That's a good idea. It would be more interesting to
ride this octopus than to use a damaged and stranded ship.
...Just do whatever you want with me... (Collapses)

--And so, with the ghostly octopus turned ally serving as
their ship, Karin and her companions headed north towards
Edo.
Phew! Haah...! We got caught in another storm...!

Just a little longer, both of you! I can see land in the
distance! There are lights too! It's not an uninhabited
island!

Come on! Show some spirit, Octopus Helper! We're almost at
the mainland... Just a little more perseverance!
Uwaaah!? The ghostly octopus is sinking...!?

It seems even the ghostly octopus has reached its limit...
What should we do now...

This is seriously bad! Does everyone know how to swim? If
the octopus sinks, we'll have to swim to shore on our own
strength!

...! I refuse to die when we're this close to Edo! Let's
resolve ourselves and swim the rest of the way!
Everyone, don't die on me! Ei! Namu san--!

...I'm sorry... I... just don't have... the strength
anymore...

Pull yourself together, Karin--! We're almost at Edo! It
would be a shame to die here!
Hold on to me! Come on, quickly!

...(Deep... sinking into the water... this sensation... a
distant memory... from somewhere before...)

You must not die! Let's survive this together, all three of
us--!

--Stamina and skill power have been \c[24]fully
restored\c[0]!
